{"id":367730,"date":[{"year":1958,"month":4,"day":30}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"工厂史专辑","genre":"","count":"413","ytitle":"","mtitle":"吊刘华","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是一位失业工人写的一首悼歌，发表在1926年3月7日出版的上海总工会三日刊上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正月里来是新春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘华本是大学生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"替我工人谋解放"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用尽心血指迷津"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二月里来暖阳阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领导我们苦演讲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级都联合"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帝国主义真吓伤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三月里来是清明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英国强盗胡乱行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常常压迫结团体"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恨得刘华怒火喷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四月里来蔷薇红"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日本厂主手段凶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"待我工人如牛马"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狠心打死顾正红"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五月里来是端阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南京路上大开枪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打死同胞无其数"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这种惨杀破天荒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六月里来热难当"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人罢工来抵抗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘华同志做领袖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不达胜利不上工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七月里来正秋凉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卖国军阀是奉张"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无故封闭总工会"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通缉刘华出赏洋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八月里来雁门关"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孙传芳带兵到上海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各国领事来接待"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提起刘华过激派"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九月里来是重阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘华捉进巡捕房"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即刻解到司令部"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"披枷带锁苦难当"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十月里来小阳春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"字林西报漏风声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘华同志遭枪毙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深更半夜暗执行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十一月里雪花飘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各工友闻讯哭号啕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"誓与刘华来报仇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"严春阳吓得不得了(注)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十二月里过年忙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"追悼刘华永不忘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"继他平生未尽志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个个来做革命党"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(注)严春阳是当时军阀统治上海时期的警察厅长。"}]}